{"word":"σταλάσσω","slug":"σταλάσσω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>σταλάσσω</b></el> <el>(στᾰλάσσω,) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to let drop</i>, <el>δάκρυ</el> <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:intransitive'>intr.</a> of things, <i>to drop, drip</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>; <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> cogn., <el>στ. φόνον</el> <i>to drop</i> blood, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>Akin to <el>στάζω.</el>\n"}]}